{"tid":1467364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日機場一事後，我有野講。","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:09.000Z","uid":82453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1725632aeea9af7b2bc714c73afa812cc2123b1a","tid":1467364,"uid":82453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"今日機場一事後，心情好沉重，只係想表達一下內心嘅感受。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>重記唔記得梁天琦嘅《致香港人的信》入面嘅一段：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「當然，真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n813當日我只係一個冷氣軍師，我無野講。但813機場一事或多或少都失民心；或許手足做錯咗，但唔緊要，錯就應、承擔責任，向咁多為受阻嘅旅客同支持我地嘅人道歉，然後再反省同檢討。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">請回想當初我地因為咩嘢而行埋一齊，<br />\n記住我地唔好變成嗰班神憎鬼厭嘅人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我真係好意鍾香港呢個地方。呢場仗，我真係唔想因為咁而輸呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割席、不譴責、不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 決一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d02541bb1aa542d1f5cb8d7ac054a6a4809c5cec","tid":1467364,"uid":82453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"求下大家 我唔想咁就輸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233af4c1eeaf1389a1587043f1ec0f9308d64be9","tid":1467364,"uid":82453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:09.000Z","msg":"團結一致就事成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}